ly have a pet sometimes and they almost never nuke, so a feel for what you can do without being spanked is needed. Same with cleric, heals and other gives aggro, and clerics nuke and stun, but not all that much. If you want an useful magician, you HAVE to try and play him alone.<br>
<br>
It is true that you know quite a bit on what different classes do, but if it was so straight forward, why is this forum here in the first place?<br>
<br>
Finally my own opinion: Botting is evil and destroys the game. I don't like it, but sometimes it is needed to do something, but I would much rather not have it there in the first place.<br>
