Aego the mage, aego it's fire pet.<br>
Train half of MM on his mage.<br>
PBAE once with the mage.<br>
Backup while the pet destroys everything.<br>
CH now and then to keep it alive.<br>
<br>
I'm not sure how he got aggro on his pet, but it worked very very nice.<br>
